# Trivy vulnerability ignore list for devbox container images.
# Add CVE IDs here to suppress false positives or accepted risks.
# Each line should contain a single CVE ID (e.g., CVE-2024-12345).
# Document the reason as a comment above each entry.

# mitmproxy transitive dependencies — waiting on mitmproxy 12.3+ to bump these.
# pyOpenSSL DTLS callback overflow — proxy only handles HTTP/HTTPS, no DTLS.
CVE-2026-27459
# tornado DoS via large multipart — proxy does not accept multipart uploads.
CVE-2026-31958

# glibc memalign overflow — base image (python:3.12-slim) ships unfixed glibc.
# Awaiting debian 13.3 update to 2.41-12+deb13u2.
CVE-2026-0861
